Package cs2030.simulator

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs2030.simulator.Event
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArriveEvent, DoneEvent, LeavesEvent, ServedEvent, ServerBackEvent, ServerRestEvent, WaitsEvent
    public abstract class Event
extends java.lang.Object
    This abstract class enforces polymorphism, whereby every event subclasses: (i) ArriveEvent, (ii) ServedEvent, (iii) WaitsEvent, (iv) LeavesEvent, (v) DoneEvent, (vi) ServerRestEvent and (vii) ServerBackEvent, inherits from this Event class. These subclasses are able to create the next event.
